OL,9,     FRover removal after a crash.
OL,10,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,11,     FThe interceptors pursue of a
OL,12,     Froadworks wrecker, a 17-year-old
OL,13,     Frobbery suspect, and a drink
OL,14,     Fdriver who doesn't understand the
OL,15,     Fword 'blow'.
OL,16,G1700 Call the Bailiffs: Time to Pay Up!
OL,17,     FIn London, Scott and police
OL,18,     Fofficers remove squatters from a
OL,19,     Fcouncil-owned building where
OL,20,     Fthey've been living for nearly a
OL,21,     Fyear. But one woman barricades
OL,22,     Fherself in a room.
