OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,7,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,8,     Funder the microscope. 84-year-old
OL,9,     FTerry, comes in with a
OL,10,     Fbadly-broken ankle and fears he
OL,11,     Fmay never dance again.
OL,12,G2100 999: Critical Condition
OL,13,     FOn the front line at Birmingham's
OL,14,     FQueen Elizabeth Hospital. A man
OL,15,     Ffalls from scaffold, impaling
OL,16,     Fhimself on a flagpole, and a
OL,17,     F73-year-old faces life-changing
OL,18,     Finjuries.
